features.name: Auto Bait
features.description: Automatically equips bait from your inventory when needed.

features.name: Auto Cast
features.description: Automatically casts your rod without any input.

features.name: Auto Debug
features.description: Runs an auto-debug during fishing to prevent fish-catching issues and automatically fixes any problems.

features.name: Auto Reel
features.description: Automatically reels in fish once hooked.

features.name: Auto Sell
features.description: Sells your fish automatically after a specified amount of time.

features.name: Auto Shake
features.description: Shakes the rod automatically when needed to ensure fish stay on the line.

features.name: Auto Totem
features.description: Automatically uses a totem from your inventory when required.

features.name: Client Optimizer
features.description: Improves game performance by boosting FPS by 50-100.

features.name: Hide Fish
features.description: Hides caught fish to prevent your inventory from filling up, improving FPS during long fishing sessions.
